prepare and submit the APP in accordance with the format approved/prescribed by the GPPB and to prepare the APP-CSE for submission to DBM-PS; 

conduct procurement planning meticulously and judiciously to avoid payments on reimbursement basis;  

subject procurements, as far as practicable, to competitive public bidding unless the conditions are present for the use of shopping or small value procurement as alternative mode of procurement; and 

resort to alternative methods of procurement only in the highly exceptional cases provided in the 2016 Revised IRR of RA No. 9184.

